latestIgtvVideos.title: Virtual Slumber Party-Lockdown Edition
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Girls just wanna have some fun. 💞👯‍♀️
We had a slumbie where all of us came dressed in our comfiest pj sets and brought food and drinks to give it all the feels. @simranbhatia111 Was spotted bringing her very own carousel filled with the slumber party essentials like Pedicure Set, patisserie, yummy snacks , sheet masks and so much more..

We hosted fun game sessions like ‘This or That’, ‘Never Have I Ever, ‘Who’s more likely to’, and ‘Rapid Fire’ respectively hosted by @simranbhatia111 @ridhishaagarwal_ @___.vinita.___ @shiyaa_sharda 

Come join us in case you missed out on the Live Session.
